---
title: North African Spiced Pumpkin & Freekeh Salad with Garlic Yoghurt & Pistachios
description: Turn a simple salad into something special with the addition of freekeh, an ancient grain that adds a toasted, nutty flavour and great texture. With mildly spiced pumpkin and a creamy garlic yoghurt, this is a substantial dinner packed with all the good stuff!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/north-african-spiced-pumpkin-freekeh-bowl-1d6fdc71.jpg
